<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Welcome to the VPN9 Affiliate Program!</h2>
    
    <p>Hi <%= @affiliate.name || @affiliate.email %>,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for joining the VPN9 Affiliate Program! We're excited to have you as a partner.</p>
    
    <h3>Your Account Details:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Affiliate Code:</strong> <%= @affiliate.code %></li>
      <li><strong>Commission Rate:</strong> <%= @affiliate.commission_rate %>%</li>
      <li><strong>Account Status:</strong> <%= @affiliate.status.capitalize %></li>
    </ul>
    
    <% if @affiliate.pending? %>
      <p>Your account is currently pending approval. We'll review your application within 24-48 hours and notify you once it's approved.</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Your account is active and ready to use! You can start promoting VPN9 immediately.</p>
    <% end %>
    
    <h3>Getting Started:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Log in to your dashboard at <%= link_to login_affiliates_url, login_affiliates_url %></li>
      <li>Get your unique referral links</li>
      <li>Start promoting VPN9 to your audience</li>
      <li>Track your performance and earnings in real-time</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our affiliate support team.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The VPN9 Team</p>
  </body>
</html>